1.0.name: wordpress/mangapress
1.0.description: Manga+Press is a webcomic managment system for WordPress. Manga+Press uses WordPress's posts, pages and categories to help you keep track of your comic posts. Manga+Press also includes its own custom template tags to help make creating themes easier.
